creator: Poupette St Barth
descriptionHtml:
Discover the latest boheme-chic outfits inspired from the beautiful Island of St Barthélémy.
Poupette St Barth, a beachwear and resortwear brand as at heart to share its passion for travel and nature through rainbow-like collections, flowery and wildlife prints for free adventurous women.

Designed by our Parisian style office, all our patterns are exclusive and make the originality of our clothes. In each collection you'll find 4 main patterns that are a visual creative symbiosis : the Floral, the Animal, the Batik and the Geometric.

Poupette St Barth is 100% handmade, only one "couturiere" composes and sews the piece giving it a unique finish.

Don't wait any longer to share "The joy of being alive"!
